description: Dedicated to fulfilling the demanding requirements of performance-conscious photographers, Transcend proudly releases its Extreme Plus 600X CompactFlash—û cards with Turbo MLC technology. Users are guaranteed to makes consecutive shooting and non-stop video recording and share their digital artwork with the world!
title: Transcend 8 GB Compact Flash Card 600X TS8GCF600
